{"id":231924505,"title":"外食族的矽膠碗選擇","content":"我是外宿兼外食的大學生\n因為外食使用的餐具量實在太可怕了😱\n一天三餐用多少紙碗、塑膠蓋、塑膠袋⋯⋯⋯⋯\n想想都覺得⋯我怎麼這麼壞(;´༎ຶД༎ຶ` )\n於是！我開始爬文尋找適合的餐具！\n\n玻璃✖️太重、不耐熱、不好攜帶\n不鏽鋼👻我覺得殼以！只是不好攜帶\n矽膠✔️✔️不過⋯要找到不容易卡味的⋯有點貴\n\n1、帕緹塔\nhttps://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkw.jpg\n爬文看人家說不太卡味道、對大學生來說超好攜帶，唯一缺點是⋯有點貴😭😭\n\n2、生活市集標榜「鉑金矽膠」\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Slriy5T.jpg\n我查過食品級矽膠和鉑金矽膠都是不錯的矽膠\n但不曉得這種碗會不會容易卡味道！也怕他會漏😭\n\n3、皇家不鏽鋼碗\nhttps://i.imgur.com/0XFANHC.jpg\n隔熱不燙手、密封不側漏🦋\n唯一缺點可能是不好攜帶（？\n\n目前找到的三名選手在此\n我真的有爬文拜託勿轟💣😅😅\n只是有點選擇障礙\n請大家給我一點建議，小女子跪謝🙇🏻‍♀️","excerpt":"我是外宿兼外食的大學生，因為外食使用的餐具量實在太可怕了，一天三餐用多少紙碗、塑膠蓋、塑膠袋⋯⋯⋯⋯，想想都覺得⋯我怎麼這麼壞（；´༎ຶД༎ຶ` ），於是！我開始爬文尋找適合的餐具！，玻璃️太重、不耐","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-24T02:37:38.956Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-24T02:40:30.391Z","commentCount":37,"likeCount":73,"tags":[],"topics":["無痕飲食","環保","愛地球","減塑","無痕"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"東海大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":73}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkw.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Slriy5T.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/0XFANHC.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c06b40c6-56eb-49be-b3aa-1d489b04f561","url":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkwl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkwl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkwl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-24T02:37:38.956Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-24T02:40:30.391Z"},{"id":"c06b40c6-56eb-49be-b3aa-1d489b04f561","url":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkw.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/WYeZRkw","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/WYeZRkwl.jpg","